  m_text: "Welcome to 1024 Escape,\nclick the Play button to enter the grid,\nbe
    prepared, as every move\nbrings the Upside Down closer,\n\nuse W A S D to shift
    the tiles,\nmerge matching numbers to grow stronger,\n\ncreate bigger tiles to
    survive,\nreach the 1024 tile to clear the game\nand escape Hawkins,\nrun out
    of moves,\nand you\u2019re lost forever. \u26A0\uFE0F"
